var book = {
	"name": "1 Corinthians",
	"numChapters": 16,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>Paul, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28348A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28348A\"></sup>called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28348B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28348B\"></sup>by the will of God to be an apostle of Christ Jesus, and our brother Sosthenes,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>To the church of God that is in Corinth, to those <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28349C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28349C\"></sup>sanctified in Christ Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28349D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28349D\"></sup>called to be saints together with all those who in every place <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28349E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28349E\"></sup>call upon the name of our Lord Jesus Christ, both their Lord and ours:",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28350F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28350F\"></sup>Grace to you and peace from God our Father and the Lord Jesus Christ.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28351G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28351G\"></sup>give thanks to my God always for you because of the grace of God that was given you in Christ Jesus,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>that in every way <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28352H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28352H\"></sup>you were enriched in him in all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28352I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28352I\"></sup>speech and all knowledge—",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>even as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28353J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28353J\"></sup>the testimony about Christ was confirmed among you—",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>so that you are not lacking in any gift, as you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28354K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28354K\"></sup>wait for the revealing of our Lord Jesus Christ,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28355L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28355L\"></sup>who will sustain you to the end, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28355M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28355M\"></sup>guiltless <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28355N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28355N\"></sup>in the day of our Lord Jesus Christ.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28356O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28356O\"></sup>God is faithful, by whom you were called into the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28356P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28356P\"></sup>fellowship of his Son, Jesus Christ our Lord.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>I appeal to you, brothers, by the name of our Lord Jesus Christ, that all of you agree, and that there be no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28357Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28357Q\"></sup>divisions among you, but that you be united <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28357R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28357R\"></sup>in the same mind and the same judgment.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For it has been reported to me by Chloe's people that there is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28358S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28358S\"></sup>quarreling among you, my brothers.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>What I mean is that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28359T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28359T\"></sup>each one of you says, “I follow Paul,” or “I follow <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28359U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28359U\"></sup>Apollos,” or “I follow <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28359V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28359V\"></sup>Cephas,” or “I follow Christ.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28360W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28360W\"></sup>Is Christ divided? Was Paul crucified for you? Or were you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28360X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28360X\"></sup>baptized in the name of Paul?",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I thank God that I baptized none of you except <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28361Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28361Y\"></sup>Crispus and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28361Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28361Z\"></sup>Gaius,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>so that no one may say that you were baptized in my name.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>(I did baptize also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28363AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28363AA\"></sup>the household of Stephanas. Beyond that, I do not know whether I baptized anyone else.)",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For Christ did not send me to baptize but to preach the gospel, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28364AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28364AB\"></sup>not with words of eloquent wisdom, lest the cross of Christ be emptied of its power.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For the word of the cross is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28365AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28365AC\"></sup>folly to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28365AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28365AD\"></sup>those who are perishing, but to us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28365AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28365AE\"></sup>who are being saved it is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28365AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28365AF\"></sup>the power of God.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>For it is written,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28366AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28366AG\"></sup>“I will destroy the wisdom of the wise,and the discernment of the discerning I will thwart.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28367AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28367AH\"></sup>Where is the one who is wise? Where is the scribe? Where is the debater of this age? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28367AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28367AI\"></sup>Has not God made foolish the wisdom of the world?",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>For since, in the wisdom of God, the world did not know God through wisdom, it pleased God through the folly of what we preach to save those who believe.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28369AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28369AJ\"></sup>Jews demand signs and Greeks seek wisdom,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>but we preach Christ <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28370AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28370AK\"></sup>crucified, a stumbling block to Jews and folly to Gentiles,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>but to those who are called, both Jews and Greeks, Christ <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28371AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28371AL\"></sup>the power of God and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28371AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28371AM\"></sup>the wisdom of God.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>For the foolishness of God is wiser than men, and the weakness of God is stronger than men.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>For consider your calling, brothers: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28373AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28373AN\"></sup>not many of you were wise according to worldly standards, not many were powerful, not many were of noble birth.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28374AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28374AO\"></sup>God chose what is foolish in the world to shame the wise; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28374AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28374AP\"></sup>God chose what is weak in the world to shame the strong;",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>God chose what is low and despised in the world, even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28375AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28375AQ\"></sup>things that are not, to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28375AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28375AR\"></sup>bring to nothing things that are,",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>so <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28376AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28376AS\"></sup>that no human being might boast in the presence of God.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>And because of him you are in Christ Jesus, who became to us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28377AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28377AT\"></sup>wisdom from God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28377AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28377AU\"></sup>righteousness and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28377AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28377AV\"></sup>sanctification and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28377AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28377AW\"></sup>redemption,",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>so that, as it is written, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28378AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28378AX\"></sup>“Let the one who boasts, boast in the Lord.”"
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>And I, when I came to you, brothers, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28379A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28379A\"></sup>did not come proclaiming to you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28379B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28379B\"></sup>the testimony of God with lofty speech or wisdom.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>For I decided to know nothing among you except <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28380C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28380C\"></sup>Jesus Christ and him crucified.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28381D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28381D\"></sup>I was with you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28381E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28381E\"></sup>in weakness and in fear and much trembling,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>and my speech and my message were not in plausible words of wisdom, but in demonstration of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28382F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28382F\"></sup>the Spirit and of power,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>so that your faith might not rest in the wisdom of men but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28383G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28383G\"></sup>in the power of God.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Yet among <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28384H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28384H\"></sup>the mature we do impart wisdom, although it is not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28384I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28384I\"></sup>a wisdom of this age or of the rulers of this age, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28384J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28384J\"></sup>who are doomed to pass away.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But we impart a secret and hidden wisdom of God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28385K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28385K\"></sup>which God decreed before the ages for our glory.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>None of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28386L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28386L\"></sup>the rulers of this age understood this, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28386M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28386M\"></sup>if they had, they would not have crucified <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28386N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28386N\"></sup>the Lord of glory.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But, as it is written,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28387O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28387O\"></sup>“What no eye has seen, nor ear heard,nor the heart of man imagined,what God has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28387P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28387P\"></sup>prepared <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28387Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28387Q\"></sup>for those who love him”—",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>these things <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28388R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28388R\"></sup>God has revealed to us through the Spirit. For the Spirit searches everything, even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28388S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28388S\"></sup>the depths of God.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For who knows a person's thoughts <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28389T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28389T\"></sup>except the spirit of that person, which is in him? So also no one comprehends the thoughts of God except the Spirit of God.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28390U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28390U\"></sup>we have received not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28390V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28390V\"></sup>the spirit of the world, but the Spirit who is from God, that we might understand the things freely given us by God.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And we impart this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28391W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28391W\"></sup>in words not taught by human wisdom but taught by the Spirit, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28391X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28391X\"></sup>interpreting spiritual truths to those who are spiritual.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The natural person does not accept the things of the Spirit of God, for they are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28392Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28392Y\"></sup>folly to him, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28392Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28392Z\"></sup>he is not able to understand them because they are spiritually discerned.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28393AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28393AA\"></sup>spiritual person judges all things, but is himself to be judged by no one.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28394AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28394AB\"></sup>“For who has understood the mind of the Lord so as to instruct him?” But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28394AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28394AC\"></sup>we have the mind of Christ."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>But I, brothers, could not address you as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28395A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28395A\"></sup>spiritual people, but as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28395B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28395B\"></sup>people of the flesh, as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28395C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28395C\"></sup>infants in Christ.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28396D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28396D\"></sup>I fed you with milk, not solid food, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28396E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28396E\"></sup>you were not ready for it. And even now you are not yet ready,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>for you are still of the flesh. For while there is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28397F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28397F\"></sup>jealousy and strife among you, are you not of the flesh and behaving only in a human way?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28398G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28398G\"></sup>when one says, “I follow Paul,” and another, “I follow Apollos,” <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28398H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28398H\"></sup>are you not being merely human?",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>What then is Apollos? What is Paul? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28399I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28399I\"></sup>Servants through whom you believed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28399J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28399J\"></sup>as the Lord assigned to each.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28400K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28400K\"></sup>I planted, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28400L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28400L\"></sup>Apollos watered, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28400M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28400M\"></sup>but God gave the growth.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28401N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28401N\"></sup>neither he who plants nor he who waters is anything, but only God who gives the growth.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>He who plants and he who waters are one, and each <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28402O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28402O\"></sup>will receive his wages according to his labor.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For we are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28403P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28403P\"></sup>God's fellow workers. You are God's field, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28403Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28403Q\"></sup>God's building.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28404R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28404R\"></sup>According to the grace of God given to me, like a skilled master builder I laid a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28404S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28404S\"></sup>foundation, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28404T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28404T\"></sup>someone else is building upon it. Let each one take care how he builds upon it.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For no one can lay a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28405U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28405U\"></sup>foundation other <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28405V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28405V\"></sup>than that which is laid, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28405W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28405W\"></sup>which is Jesus Christ.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Now if anyone builds on the foundation with gold, silver, precious stones, wood, hay, straw—",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28407X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28407X\"></sup>each one's work will become manifest, for the Day will disclose it, because it will be revealed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28407Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28407Y\"></sup>by fire, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28407Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28407Z\"></sup>the fire will test what sort of work each one has done.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>If the work that anyone has built on the foundation survives, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28408AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28408AA\"></sup>he will receive a reward.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>If anyone's work is burned up, he will suffer loss, though he himself will be saved, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28409AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28409AB\"></sup>but only as through fire.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28410AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28410AC\"></sup>Do you not know that you are God's temple and that God's Spirit dwells in you?",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>If anyone destroys God's temple, God will destroy him. For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28411AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28411AD\"></sup>God's temple is holy, and you are that temple.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28412AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28412AE\"></sup>Let no one deceive himself. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28412AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28412AF\"></sup>If anyone among you thinks that he is wise in this age, let him become a fool that he may become wise.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28413AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28413AG\"></sup>the wisdom of this world is folly with God. For it is written, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28413AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28413AH\"></sup>“He catches the wise in their craftiness,”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>and again, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28414AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28414AI\"></sup>“The Lord knows the thoughts of the wise, that they are futile.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28415AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28415AJ\"></sup>let no one boast in men. For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28415AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28415AK\"></sup>all things are yours,",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>whether Paul or Apollos or Cephas or the world or life or death or the present or the future—all are yours,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28417AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28417AL\"></sup>you are Christ's, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28417AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28417AM\"></sup>Christ is God's."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>This is how one should regard us, as servants of Christ and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28418A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28418A\"></sup>stewards of the mysteries of God.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Moreover, it is required of stewards that they be found faithful.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>But with me it is a very small thing that I should be judged by you or by any human court. In fact, I do not even judge myself.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28421B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28421B\"></sup>For I am not aware of anything against myself, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28421C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28421C\"></sup>but I am not thereby acquitted. It is the Lord who judges me.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28422D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28422D\"></sup>do not pronounce judgment before the time, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28422E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28422E\"></sup>before the Lord comes, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28422F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28422F\"></sup>who will bring to light the things now hidden in darkness and will disclose the purposes of the heart. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28422G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28422G\"></sup>Then each one will receive his commendation from God.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>I have applied all these things to myself and Apollos for your benefit, brothers, that you may learn by us not to go beyond what is written, that none of you may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28423H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28423H\"></sup>be puffed up in favor of one against another.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>For who sees anything different in you? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28424I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28424I\"></sup>What do you have that you did not receive? If then you received it, why do you boast as if you did not receive it?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Already you have all you want! Already you have become rich! Without us you have become kings! And would that you did reign, so that we might share the rule with you!",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For I think that God has exhibited us apostles as last of all, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28426J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28426J\"></sup>like men sentenced to death, because we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28426K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28426K\"></sup>have become a spectacle to the world, to angels, and to men.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28427L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28427L\"></sup>We are fools for Christ's sake, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28427M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28427M\"></sup>you are wise in Christ. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28427N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28427N\"></sup>We are weak, but you are strong. You are held in honor, but we in disrepute.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>To the present hour <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28428O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28428O\"></sup>we hunger and thirst, we are poorly dressed and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28428P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28428P\"></sup>buffeted and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28428Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28428Q\"></sup>homeless,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>and we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28429R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28429R\"></sup>labor, working with our own hands. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28429S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28429S\"></sup>When reviled, we bless; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28429T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28429T\"></sup>when persecuted, we endure;",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>when slandered, we entreat. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28430U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28430U\"></sup>We have become, and are still, like the scum of the world, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28430V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28430V\"></sup>the refuse of all things.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I do not write these things <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28431W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28431W\"></sup>to make you ashamed, but to admonish you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28431X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28431X\"></sup>as my beloved children.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28432Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28432Y\"></sup>though you have countless guides in Christ, you do not have many fathers. For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28432Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28432Z\"></sup>I became your father in Christ Jesus through the gospel.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>I urge you, then, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28433AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28433AA\"></sup>be imitators of me.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>That is why <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28434AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28434AB\"></sup>I sent you Timothy, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28434AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28434AC\"></sup>my beloved and faithful child in the Lord, to remind you of my ways in Christ, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28434AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28434AD\"></sup>as I teach them everywhere in every church.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Some are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28435AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28435AE\"></sup>arrogant, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28435AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28435AF\"></sup>as though I were not coming to you.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28436AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28436AG\"></sup>I will come to you soon, if the Lord wills, and I will find out not the talk of these arrogant people but their power.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28437AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28437AH\"></sup>the kingdom of God does not consist in talk but in power.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>What do you wish? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28438AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28438AI\"></sup>Shall I come to you with a rod, or with love in a spirit of gentleness?"
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>It is actually reported that there is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28439A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28439A\"></sup>sexual immorality among you, and of a kind that is not tolerated even among pagans, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28439B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28439B\"></sup>for a man has his father's wife.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28440C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28440C\"></sup>you are arrogant! Ought you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28440D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28440D\"></sup>not rather to mourn? Let him who has done this be removed from among you.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For though <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28441E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28441E\"></sup>absent in body, I am present in spirit; and as if present, I have already pronounced judgment on the one who did such a thing.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>When you are assembled <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28442F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28442F\"></sup>in the name of the Lord Jesus and my spirit is present, with the power of our Lord Jesus,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28443G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28443G\"></sup>to deliver this man to Satan for the destruction of the flesh, so <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28443H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28443H\"></sup>that his spirit may be saved <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28443I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28443I\"></sup>in the day of the Lord.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28444J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28444J\"></sup>Your boasting is not good. Do you not know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28444K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28444K\"></sup>a little leaven leavens the whole lump?",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Cleanse out the old leaven that you may be a new lump, as you really are unleavened. For Christ, our Passover lamb, has been sacrificed.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Let us therefore celebrate the festival, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28446L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28446L\"></sup>not with the old leaven, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28446M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28446M\"></sup>the leaven of malice and evil, but with the unleavened bread of sincerity and truth.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>I wrote to you in my letter <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28447N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28447N\"></sup>not to associate with sexually immoral people—",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28448O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28448O\"></sup>not at all meaning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28448P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28448P\"></sup>the sexually immoral of this world, or the greedy and swindlers, or idolaters, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28448Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28448Q\"></sup>since then you would need to go out of the world.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But now I am writing to you not to associate with anyone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28449R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28449R\"></sup>who bears the name of brother if he is guilty of sexual immorality or greed, or is an idolater, reviler, drunkard, or swindler—not even to eat with such a one.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For what have I to do with judging <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28450S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28450S\"></sup>outsiders? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28450T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28450T\"></sup>Is it not those inside the church whom you are to judge?",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>God judges those outside. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28451U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28451U\"></sup>“Purge the evil person from among you.”"
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>When one of you has a grievance against another, does he dare go to law before the unrighteous <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28452A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28452A\"></sup>instead of the saints?",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Or do you not know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28453B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28453B\"></sup>the saints will judge the world? And if the world is to be judged by you, are you incompetent to try trivial cases?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Do you not know that we are to judge angels? How much more, then, matters pertaining to this life!",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>So if you have such cases, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28455C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28455C\"></sup>why do you lay them before those who have no standing in the church?",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28456D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28456D\"></sup>I say this to your shame. Can it be that there is no one among you wise enough to settle a dispute between the brothers,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>but brother goes to law against brother, and that before unbelievers?",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>To have lawsuits at all with one another is already a defeat for you. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28458E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28458E\"></sup>Why not rather suffer wrong? Why not rather be defrauded?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But you yourselves wrong and defraud—even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28459F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28459F\"></sup>your own brothers!",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Or do you not know that the unrighteous will not inherit the kingdom of God? Do not be deceived: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28460G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28460G\"></sup>neither the sexually immoral, nor idolaters, nor adulterers, nor men who practice homosexuality,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>nor thieves, nor the greedy, nor drunkards, nor revilers, nor swindlers will inherit the kingdom of God.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28462H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28462H\"></sup>such were some of you. But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28462I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28462I\"></sup>you were washed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28462J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28462J\"></sup>you were sanctified, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28462K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28462K\"></sup>you were justified in the name of the Lord Jesus Christ and by the Spirit of our God.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28463L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28463L\"></sup>“All things are lawful for me,” but not all things are helpful. “All things are lawful for me,” but I will not be dominated by anything.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28464M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28464M\"></sup>“Food is meant for the stomach and the stomach for food”—and God will destroy both one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28464N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28464N\"></sup>and the other. The body is not meant for sexual immorality, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28464O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28464O\"></sup>for the Lord, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28464P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28464P\"></sup>the Lord for the body.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28465Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28465Q\"></sup>God raised the Lord and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28465R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28465R\"></sup>will also raise us up <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28465S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28465S\"></sup>by his power.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Do you not know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28466T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28466T\"></sup>your bodies are members of Christ? Shall I then take the members of Christ and make them members of a prostitute? Never!",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Or do you not know that he who is joined to a prostitute becomes one body with her? For, as it is written, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28467U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28467U\"></sup>“The two will become one flesh.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>But he who is joined to the Lord <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28468V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28468V\"></sup>becomes one spirit with him.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28469W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28469W\"></sup>Flee from sexual immorality. Every other sin a person commits is outside the body, but the sexually immoral person <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28469X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28469X\"></sup>sins against his own body.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28470Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28470Y\"></sup>do you not know that your body is a temple of the Holy Spirit within you, whom you have from God? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28470Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28470Z\"></sup>You are not your own,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28471AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28471AA\"></sup>for you were bought with a price. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28471AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28471AB\"></sup>So glorify God in your body."
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span>Now concerning the matters about which you wrote: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28472A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28472A\"></sup>“It is good for a man not to have sexual relations with a woman.”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>But because of the temptation to sexual immorality, each man should have his own wife and each woman her own husband.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28474B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28474B\"></sup>The husband should give to his wife her conjugal rights, and likewise the wife to her husband.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For the wife does not have authority over her own body, but the husband does. Likewise the husband does not have authority over his own body, but the wife does.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28476C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28476C\"></sup>Do not deprive one another, except perhaps by agreement for a limited time, that you may devote yourselves to prayer; but then come together again, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28476D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28476D\"></sup>so that Satan may not tempt you because of your lack of self-control.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Now as a concession, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28477E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28477E\"></sup>not a command, I say this.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28478F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28478F\"></sup>I wish that all were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28478G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28478G\"></sup>as I myself am. But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28478H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28478H\"></sup>each has his own gift from God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28478I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28478I\"></sup>one of one kind and one of another.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>To the unmarried and the widows I say that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28479J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28479J\"></sup>it is good for them to remain single, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28479K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28479K\"></sup>as I am.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But if they cannot exercise self-control, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28480L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28480L\"></sup>they should marry. For it is better to marry than to burn with passion.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>To the married <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28481M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28481M\"></sup>I give this charge (not I, but the Lord): <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28481N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28481N\"></sup>the wife should not separate from her husband",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>(but if she does, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28482O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28482O\"></sup>she should remain unmarried or else be reconciled to her husband), and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28482P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28482P\"></sup>the husband should not divorce his wife.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>To the rest I say (I, not the Lord) that if any brother has a wife who is an unbeliever, and she consents to live with him, he should not divorce her.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>If any woman has a husband who is an unbeliever, and he consents to live with her, she should not divorce him.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For the unbelieving husband is made holy because of his wife, and the unbelieving wife is made holy because of her husband. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28485Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28485Q\"></sup>Otherwise your children would be unclean, but as it is, they are holy.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>But if the unbelieving partner separates, let it be so. In such cases the brother or sister is not enslaved. God has called you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28486R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28486R\"></sup>to peace.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For how do you know, wife, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28487S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28487S\"></sup>whether you will save your husband? Or how do you know, husband, whether you will save your wife?",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Only let each person lead the life <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28488T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28488T\"></sup>that the Lord has assigned to him, and to which God has called him. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28488U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28488U\"></sup>This is my rule in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28488V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28488V\"></sup>all the churches.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Was anyone at the time of his call already circumcised? Let him not seek to remove the marks of circumcision. Was anyone at the time of his call uncircumcised? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28489W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28489W\"></sup>Let him not seek circumcision.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28490X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28490X\"></sup>For neither circumcision counts for anything nor uncircumcision, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28490Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28490Y\"></sup>keeping the commandments of God.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28491Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28491Z\"></sup>Each one should remain in the condition in which he was called.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Were you a bondservant when called? Do not be concerned about it. (But if you can gain your freedom, avail yourself of the opportunity.)",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>For he who was called in the Lord as a bondservant is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28493AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28493AA\"></sup>a freedman of the Lord. Likewise he who was free when called is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28493AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28493AB\"></sup>a bondservant of Christ.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28494AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28494AC\"></sup>You were bought with a price; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28494AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28494AD\"></sup>do not become bondservants of men.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>So, brothers, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28495AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28495AE\"></sup>in whatever condition each was called, there let him remain with God.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Now concerning the betrothed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28496AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28496AF\"></sup>I have no command from the Lord, but I give my judgment as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28496AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28496AG\"></sup>one who by the Lord's mercy is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28496AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28496AH\"></sup>trustworthy.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>I think that in view of the present distress <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28497AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28497AI\"></sup>it is good for a person to remain as he is.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Are you bound to a wife? Do not seek to be free. Are you free from a wife? Do not seek a wife.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>But if you do marry, you have not sinned, and if a betrothed woman marries, she has not sinned. Yet those who marry will have worldly troubles, and I would spare you that.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>This is what I mean, brothers: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28500AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28500AJ\"></sup>the appointed time has grown very short. From now on, let those who have wives live as though they had none,",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>and those who mourn as though they were not mourning, and those who rejoice as though they were not rejoicing, and those who buy <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28501AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28501AK\"></sup>as though they had no goods,",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>and those who deal with the world as though they had no dealings with it. For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28502AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28502AL\"></sup>the present form of this world is passing away.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>I want you to be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28503AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28503AM\"></sup>free from anxieties. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28503AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28503AN\"></sup>The unmarried man is anxious about the things of the Lord, how to please the Lord.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>But the married man is anxious about worldly things, how to please his wife,",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>and his interests are divided. And the unmarried or betrothed woman is anxious about the things of the Lord, how to be holy in body and spirit. But the married woman is anxious about worldly things, how to please her husband.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>I say this for your own benefit, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28506AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28506AO\"></sup>not to lay any restraint upon you, but to promote good order and to secure your undivided devotion to the Lord.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>If anyone thinks that he is not behaving properly toward his betrothed, if his passions are strong, and it has to be, let him do as he wishes: let them marry—it is no sin.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>But whoever is firmly established in his heart, being under no necessity but having his desire under control, and has determined this in his heart, to keep her as his betrothed, he will do well.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>So then he who marries his betrothed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28509AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28509AP\"></sup>does well, and he who refrains from marriage will do even better.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28510AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28510AQ\"></sup>A wife is bound to her husband as long as he lives. But if her husband dies, she is free to be married to whom she wishes, only <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28510AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28510AR\"></sup>in the Lord.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>Yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28511AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28511AS\"></sup>in my judgment she is happier if she remains as she is. And I think <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28511AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28511AT\"></sup>that I too have the Spirit of God."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span>Now concerning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28512A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28512A\"></sup>food offered to idols: we know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28512B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28512B\"></sup>“all of us possess knowledge.” This “knowledge” <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28512C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28512C\"></sup>puffs up, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28512D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28512D\"></sup>but love builds up.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28513E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28513E\"></sup>If anyone imagines that he knows something, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28513F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28513F\"></sup>he does not yet know as he ought to know.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>But if anyone loves God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28514G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28514G\"></sup>he is known by God.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Therefore, as to the eating of food offered to idols, we know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28515H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28515H\"></sup>“an idol has no real existence,” and that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28515I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28515I\"></sup>“there is no God but one.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For although there may be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28516J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28516J\"></sup>so-called gods in heaven or on earth—as indeed there are many “gods” and many “lords”—",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28517K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28517K\"></sup>for us there is one God, the Father, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28517L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28517L\"></sup>from whom are all things and for whom we exist, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28517M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28517M\"></sup>one Lord, Jesus Christ, through whom are all things and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28517N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28517N\"></sup>through whom we exist.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>However, not all possess this knowledge. But some, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28518O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28518O\"></sup>through former association with idols, eat food as really offered to an idol, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28518P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28518P\"></sup>their conscience, being weak, is defiled.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28519Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28519Q\"></sup>Food will not commend us to God. We are no worse off if we do not eat, and no better off if we do.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But take care <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28520R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28520R\"></sup>that this right of yours does not somehow become a stumbling block <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28520S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28520S\"></sup>to the weak.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For if anyone sees you who have knowledge eating in an idol's temple, will he not be encouraged, if his conscience is weak, to eat food offered to idols?",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And so by your knowledge this weak person is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28522T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28522T\"></sup>destroyed, the brother for whom Christ died.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Thus, sinning against your brothers and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28523U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28523U\"></sup>wounding their conscience when it is weak, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28523V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28523V\"></sup>you sin against Christ.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Therefore, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28524W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28524W\"></sup>if food makes my brother stumble, I will never eat meat, lest I make my brother stumble."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">9 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28525A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28525A\"></sup>Am I not free? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28525B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28525B\"></sup>Am I not an apostle? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28525C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28525C\"></sup>Have I not seen Jesus our Lord? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28525D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28525D\"></sup>Are not you my workmanship in the Lord?",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>If to others I am not an apostle, at least I am to you, for you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28526E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28526E\"></sup>the seal of my apostleship in the Lord.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>This is my defense to those who would examine me.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28528F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28528F\"></sup>Do we not have the right to eat and drink?",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28529G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28529G\"></sup>Do we not have the right to take along a believing wife, as do the other apostles and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28529H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28529H\"></sup>the brothers of the Lord and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28529I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28529I\"></sup>Cephas?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Or is it only Barnabas and I who have no right to refrain from working for a living?",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28531J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28531J\"></sup>Who serves as a soldier at his own expense? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28531K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28531K\"></sup>Who plants a vineyard without eating any of its fruit? Or who tends a flock without getting some of the milk?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Do I say these things on human authority? Does not the Law say the same?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For it is written in the Law of Moses, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28533L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28533L\"></sup>“You shall not muzzle an ox when it treads out the grain.” Is it for oxen that God is concerned?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Does he not certainly speak for our sake? It was written <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28534M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28534M\"></sup>for our sake, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28534N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28534N\"></sup>the plowman should plow in hope and the thresher thresh in hope of sharing in the crop.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28535O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28535O\"></sup>If we have sown spiritual things among you, is it too much if we reap material things from you?",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>If others share this rightful claim on you, do not we even more?Nevertheless, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28536P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28536P\"></sup>we have not made use of this right, but we endure anything <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28536Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28536Q\"></sup>rather than put an obstacle in the way of the gospel of Christ.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Do you not know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28537R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28537R\"></sup>those who are employed in the temple service get their food from the temple, and those who serve at the altar share in the sacrificial offerings?",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>In the same way, the Lord commanded that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28538S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28538S\"></sup>those who proclaim the gospel should get their living by the gospel.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28539T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28539T\"></sup>I have made no use of any of these rights, nor am I writing these things to secure any such provision. For I would rather die than have anyone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28539U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28539U\"></sup>deprive me of my ground for boasting.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For if I preach the gospel, that gives me no ground for boasting. For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28540V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28540V\"></sup>necessity is laid upon me. Woe to me if I do not preach the gospel!",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For if I do this of my own will, I have a reward, but if not of my own will, I am still entrusted with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28541W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28541W\"></sup>a stewardship.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>What then is my reward? That in my preaching <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28542X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28542X\"></sup>I may present the gospel free of charge, so as not to make full use of my right in the gospel.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28543Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28543Y\"></sup>though I am free from all, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28543Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28543Z\"></sup>I have made myself a servant to all, that I might <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28543AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28543AA\"></sup>win more of them.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28544AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28544AB\"></sup>To the Jews I became as a Jew, in order to win Jews. To those under the law I became as one under the law (though not being myself under the law) that I might win those under the law.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>To <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28545AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28545AC\"></sup>those outside the law I became <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28545AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28545AD\"></sup>as one outside the law (not being outside the law of God but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28545AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28545AE\"></sup>under the law of Christ) that I might win those outside the law.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28546AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28546AF\"></sup>To the weak I became weak, that I might win the weak. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28546AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28546AG\"></sup>I have become all things to all people, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28546AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28546AH\"></sup>by all means I might save some.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>I do it all for the sake of the gospel, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28547AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28547AI\"></sup>that I may share with them in its blessings.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Do you not know that in a race all the runners run, but only one receives <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28548AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28548AJ\"></sup>the prize? So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28548AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28548AK\"></sup>run that you may obtain it.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Every <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28549AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28549AL\"></sup>athlete exercises self-control in all things. They do it to receive a perishable wreath, but we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28549AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28549AM\"></sup>an imperishable.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>So I do not run aimlessly; I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28550AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28550AN\"></sup>do not box as one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28550AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28550AO\"></sup>beating the air.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>But I discipline my body and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28551AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28551AP\"></sup>keep it under control, lest after preaching to others <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28551AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28551AQ\"></sup>I myself should be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28551AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28551AR\"></sup>disqualified."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">10 </span>For I do not want you to be unaware, brothers, that our fathers were all under <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28552A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28552A\"></sup>the cloud, and all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28552B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28552B\"></sup>passed through the sea,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and all were baptized into Moses in the cloud and in the sea,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28554C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28554C\"></sup>all ate the same <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28554D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28554D\"></sup>spiritual food,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28555E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28555E\"></sup>all drank the same spiritual drink. For they drank from the spiritual Rock that followed them, and the Rock was Christ.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Nevertheless, with most of them God was not pleased, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28556F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28556F\"></sup>they were overthrown in the wilderness.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Now these things took place as examples for us, that we might not desire evil as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28557G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28557G\"></sup>they did.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28558H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28558H\"></sup>Do not be idolaters <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28558I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28558I\"></sup>as some of them were; as it is written, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28558J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28558J\"></sup>“The people sat down to eat and drink and rose up to play.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28559K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28559K\"></sup>We must not indulge in sexual immorality <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28559L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28559L\"></sup>as some of them did, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28559M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28559M\"></sup>twenty-three thousand fell in a single day.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>We must not put Christ to the test, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28560N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28560N\"></sup>as some of them did and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28560O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28560O\"></sup>were destroyed by serpents,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>nor grumble, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28561P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28561P\"></sup>as some of them did and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28561Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28561Q\"></sup>were destroyed by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28561R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28561R\"></sup>the Destroyer.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Now these things happened to them as an example, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28562S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28562S\"></sup>they were written down for our instruction, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28562T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28562T\"></sup>on whom the end of the ages has come.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28563U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28563U\"></sup>let anyone who thinks that he stands take heed lest he fall.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>No temptation has overtaken you that is not common to man. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28564V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28564V\"></sup>God is faithful, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28564W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28564W\"></sup>he will not let you be tempted beyond your ability, but with the temptation he will also provide the way of escape, that you may be able to endure it.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Therefore, my beloved, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28565X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28565X\"></sup>flee from idolatry.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>I speak <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28566Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28566Y\"></sup>as to sensible people; judge for yourselves what I say.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28567Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28567Z\"></sup>The cup of blessing that we bless, is it not a participation in the blood of Christ? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28567AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28567AA\"></sup>The bread that we break, is it not a participation in the body of Christ?",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Because there is one bread, we who are many are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28568AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28568AB\"></sup>one body, for we all partake of the one bread.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Consider <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28569AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28569AC\"></sup>the people of Israel: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28569AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28569AD\"></sup>are not those who eat the sacrifices participants in the altar?",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>What do I imply then? That food offered to idols is anything, or that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28570AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28570AE\"></sup>an idol is anything?",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>No, I imply that what pagans sacrifice <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28571AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28571AF\"></sup>they offer to demons and not to God. I do not want you to be participants with demons.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28572AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28572AG\"></sup>You cannot drink the cup of the Lord and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28572AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28572AH\"></sup>the cup of demons. You cannot partake of the table of the Lord and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28572AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28572AI\"></sup>the table of demons.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28573AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28573AJ\"></sup>Shall we provoke the Lord to jealousy? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28573AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28573AK\"></sup>Are we stronger than he?",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28574AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28574AL\"></sup>“All things are lawful,” but not all things are helpful. “All things are lawful,” but not all things build up.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28575AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28575AM\"></sup>Let no one seek his own good, but the good of his neighbor.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28576AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28576AN\"></sup>Eat whatever is sold in the meat market without raising any question on the ground of conscience.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28577AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28577AO\"></sup>“the earth is the Lord's, and the fullness thereof.”",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>If one of the unbelievers invites you to dinner and you are disposed to go, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28578AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28578AP\"></sup>eat whatever is set before you without raising any question on the ground of conscience.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>But if someone says to you, “This has been offered in sacrifice,” then do not eat it, for the sake of the one who informed you, and for the sake of conscience—",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>I do not mean <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28580AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28580AQ\"></sup>your conscience, but his. For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28580AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28580AR\"></sup>why should my liberty be determined by someone else's conscience?",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>If I partake with thankfulness, why am I denounced because of that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28581AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28581AS\"></sup>for which I give thanks?",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>So, whether you eat or drink, or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28582AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28582AT\"></sup>whatever you do, do all to the glory of God.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28583AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28583AU\"></sup>Give no offense to Jews or to Greeks or to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28583AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28583AV\"></sup>the church of God,",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>just as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28584AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28584AW\"></sup>I try to please everyone in everything I do, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28584AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28584AX\"></sup>not seeking my own advantage, but that of many, that they may be saved."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">11 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28585A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28585A\"></sup>Be imitators of me, as I am of Christ.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Now I commend you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28586B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28586B\"></sup>because you remember me in everything and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28586C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28586C\"></sup>maintain the traditions <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28586D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28586D\"></sup>even as I delivered them to you.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>But I want you to understand that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28587E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28587E\"></sup>the head of every man is Christ, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28587F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28587F\"></sup>the head of a wife is her husband, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28587G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28587G\"></sup>the head of Christ is God.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Every man who prays or prophesies with his head covered dishonors his head,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>but every wife who prays or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28589H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28589H\"></sup>prophesies <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28589I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28589I\"></sup>with her head uncovered dishonors her head, since it is the same <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28589J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28589J\"></sup>as if her head were shaven.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For if a wife will not cover her head, then she should cut her hair short. But since it is disgraceful for a wife to cut off her hair or shave her head, let her cover her head.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>For a man ought not to cover his head, since <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28591K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28591K\"></sup>he is the image and glory of God, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28591L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28591L\"></sup>woman is the glory of man.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28592M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28592M\"></sup>man was not made from woman, but woman from man.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Neither was man created for woman, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28593N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28593N\"></sup>woman for man.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>That is why a wife ought to have a symbol of authority on her head, because of the angels.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Nevertheless, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28595O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28595O\"></sup>in the Lord woman is not independent of man nor man of woman;",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>for as woman was made from man, so man is now born of woman. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28596P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28596P\"></sup>all things are from God.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Judge for yourselves: is it proper for a wife to pray to God with her head uncovered?",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Does not nature itself teach you that if a man wears long hair it is a disgrace for him,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>but if a woman has long hair, it is her glory? For her hair is given to her for a covering.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28600Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28600Q\"></sup>If anyone is inclined to be contentious, we have no such practice, nor do <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28600R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28600R\"></sup>the churches of God.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>But in the following instructions I do not commend you, because when you come together it is not for the better but for the worse.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For, in the first place, when you come together as a church, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28602S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28602S\"></sup>I hear that there are divisions among you. And I believe it in part,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28603T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28603T\"></sup>there must be factions among you in order <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28603U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28603U\"></sup>that those who are genuine among you may be recognized.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>When you come together, it is not the Lord's supper that you eat.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>For in eating, each one goes ahead with his own meal. One goes hungry, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28605V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28605V\"></sup>another gets drunk.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>What! Do you not have houses to eat and drink in? Or do you despise <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28606W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28606W\"></sup>the church of God and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28606X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28606X\"></sup>humiliate those who have nothing? What shall I say to you? Shall I commend you in this? No, I will not.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28607Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28607Y\"></sup>I received from the Lord what I also delivered to you, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28607Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28607Z\"></sup>the Lord Jesus on the night when he was betrayed took bread,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>and when he had given thanks, he broke it, and said, <span class=\"woj\">“This is my body, which is for you. Do this in remembrance of me.”</span>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>In the same way also he took the cup, after supper, saying, <span class=\"woj\">“This cup is the new covenant in my blood. Do this, as often as you drink it, in remembrance of me.”</span>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>For as often as you eat this bread and drink the cup, you proclaim the Lord's death <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28610AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28610AA\"></sup>until he comes.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28611AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28611AB\"></sup>Whoever, therefore, eats the bread or drinks the cup of the Lord <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28611AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28611AC\"></sup>in an unworthy manner will be guilty concerning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28611AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28611AD\"></sup>the body and blood of the Lord.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28612AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28612AE\"></sup>Let a person examine himself, then, and so eat of the bread and drink of the cup.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>For anyone who eats and drinks without discerning the body eats and drinks judgment on himself.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>That is why many of you are weak and ill, and some <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28614AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28614AF\"></sup>have died.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28615AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28615AG\"></sup>But if we judged ourselves truly, we would not be judged.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>But when we are judged by the Lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28616AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28616AH\"></sup>we are disciplined so that we may not be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28616AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28616AI\"></sup>condemned along with the world.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>So then, my brothers, when you come together to eat, wait for one another—",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28618AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28618AJ\"></sup>if anyone is hungry, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28618AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28618AK\"></sup>let him eat at home—so that when you come together it will not be for judgment. About the other things <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28618AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28618AL\"></sup>I will give directions <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28618AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28618AM\"></sup>when I come."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">12 </span>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28619A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28619A\"></sup>concerning spiritual gifts, brothers, I do not want you to be uninformed.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>You know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28620B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28620B\"></sup>when you were pagans <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28620C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28620C\"></sup>you were led astray to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28620D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28620D\"></sup>mute idols, however you were led.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Therefore I want you to understand that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28621E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28621E\"></sup>no one speaking in the Spirit of God ever says “Jesus is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28621F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28621F\"></sup>accursed!” and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28621G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28621G\"></sup>no one can say “Jesus is Lord” except in the Holy Spirit.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28622H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28622H\"></sup>there are varieties of gifts, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28622I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28622I\"></sup>the same Spirit;",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28623J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28623J\"></sup>there are varieties of service, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28623K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28623K\"></sup>the same Lord;",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>and there are varieties of activities, but it is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28624L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28624L\"></sup>the same God who empowers them all in everyone.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28625M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28625M\"></sup>To each is given the manifestation of the Spirit for the common good.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For to one is given through the Spirit the utterance of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28626N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28626N\"></sup>wisdom, and to another the utterance of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28626O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28626O\"></sup>knowledge according to the same Spirit,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>to another <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28627P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28627P\"></sup>faith by the same Spirit, to another <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28627Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28627Q\"></sup>gifts of healing by the one Spirit,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>to another <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28628R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28628R\"></sup>the working of miracles, to another <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28628S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28628S\"></sup>prophecy, to another <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28628T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28628T\"></sup>the ability to distinguish between spirits, to another <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28628U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28628U\"></sup>various kinds of tongues, to another <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28628V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28628V\"></sup>the interpretation of tongues.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>All these are empowered by one and the same Spirit, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28629W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28629W\"></sup>who apportions to each one individually <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28629X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28629X\"></sup>as he wills.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For just as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28630Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28630Y\"></sup>the body is one and has many members, and all the members of the body, though many, are one body, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28630Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28630Z\"></sup>so it is with Christ.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28631AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28631AA\"></sup>in one Spirit we were all baptized into one body—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28631AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28631AB\"></sup>Jews or Greeks, slaves or free—and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28631AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28631AC\"></sup>all were made to drink of one Spirit.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For the body does not consist of one member but of many.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>If the foot should say, “Because I am not a hand, I do not belong to the body,” that would not make it any less a part of the body.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And if the ear should say, “Because I am not an eye, I do not belong to the body,” that would not make it any less a part of the body.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>If the whole body were an eye, where would be the sense of hearing? If the whole body were an ear, where would be the sense of smell?",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>But as it is, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28636AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28636AD\"></sup>God arranged the members in the body, each one of them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28636AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28636AE\"></sup>as he chose.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>If all were a single member, where would the body be?",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>As it is, there are many parts, yet one body.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>The eye cannot say to the hand, “I have no need of you,” nor again the head to the feet, “I have no need of you.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>On the contrary, the parts of the body that seem to be weaker are indispensable,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>and on those parts of the body that we think less honorable we bestow the greater honor, and our unpresentable parts are treated with greater modesty,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>which our more presentable parts do not require. But God has so composed the body, giving greater honor to the part that lacked it,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>that there may be no division in the body, but that the members may have the same care for one another.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>If one member suffers, all suffer together; if one member is honored, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28644AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28644AF\"></sup>all rejoice together.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28645AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28645AG\"></sup>you are the body of Christ and individually <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28645AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28645AH\"></sup>members of it.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28646AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28646AI\"></sup>God has appointed in the church first <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28646AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28646AJ\"></sup>apostles, second <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28646AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28646AK\"></sup>prophets, third teachers, then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28646AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28646AL\"></sup>miracles, then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28646AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28646AM\"></sup>gifts of healing, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28646AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28646AN\"></sup>helping, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28646AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28646AO\"></sup>administrating, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28646AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28646AP\"></sup>various kinds of tongues.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Are all apostles? Are all prophets? Are all teachers? Do all work miracles?",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Do all possess gifts of healing? Do all speak with tongues? Do all interpret?",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28649AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28649AQ\"></sup>earnestly desire the higher gifts.And I will show you a still more excellent way."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">13 </span>If I speak in the tongues of men and of angels, but have not love, I am a noisy gong or a clanging cymbal.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And if I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28651A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28651A\"></sup>prophetic powers, and understand all mysteries and all knowledge, and if I have all faith, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28651B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28651B\"></sup>so as to remove mountains, but have not love, I am nothing.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28652C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28652C\"></sup>If I give away all I have, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28652D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28652D\"></sup>if I deliver up my body to be burned, but have not love, I gain nothing.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28653E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28653E\"></sup>Love is patient and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28653F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28653F\"></sup>kind; love <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28653G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28653G\"></sup>does not envy or boast; it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28653H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28653H\"></sup>is not arrogant",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>or rude. It <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28654I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28654I\"></sup>does not insist on its own way; it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28654J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28654J\"></sup>is not irritable or resentful;",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28655K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28655K\"></sup>does not rejoice at wrongdoing, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28655L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28655L\"></sup>rejoices with the truth.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28656M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28656M\"></sup>Love bears all things, believes all things, hopes all things, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28656N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28656N\"></sup>endures all things.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Love never ends. As for prophecies, they will pass away; as for tongues, they will cease; as for knowledge, it will pass away.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28658O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28658O\"></sup>we know in part and we prophesy in part,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28659P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28659P\"></sup>when the perfect comes, the partial will pass away.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>When I was a child, I spoke like a child, I thought like a child, I reasoned like a child. When I became a man, I gave up childish ways.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28661Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28661Q\"></sup>now we see in a mirror dimly, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28661R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28661R\"></sup>then face to face. Now I know in part; then I shall know fully, even as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28661S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28661S\"></sup>I have been fully known.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>So now faith, hope, and love abide, these three; but the greatest of these is love."
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">14 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28663A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28663A\"></sup>Pursue love, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28663B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28663B\"></sup>earnestly desire the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28663C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28663C\"></sup>spiritual gifts, especially that you may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28663D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28663D\"></sup>prophesy.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28664E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28664E\"></sup>one who speaks in a tongue speaks not to men but to God; for no one understands him, but he utters mysteries in the Spirit.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>On the other hand, the one who prophesies speaks to people for their upbuilding and encouragement and consolation.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The one who speaks in a tongue builds up himself, but the one who prophesies builds up the church.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Now I want you all to speak in tongues, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28667F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28667F\"></sup>even more to prophesy. The one who prophesies is greater than the one who speaks in tongues, unless someone interprets, so that the church may be built up.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Now, brothers, if I come to you speaking in tongues, how will I benefit you unless I bring you some <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28668G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28668G\"></sup>revelation or knowledge or prophecy or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28668H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28668H\"></sup>teaching?",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>If even lifeless instruments, such as the flute or the harp, do not give distinct notes, how will anyone know what is played?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28670I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28670I\"></sup>if the bugle gives an indistinct sound, who will get ready for battle?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>So with yourselves, if with your tongue you utter speech that is not intelligible, how will anyone know what is said? For you will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28671J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28671J\"></sup>speaking into the air.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>There are doubtless many different languages in the world, and none is without meaning,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>but if I do not know the meaning of the language, I will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28673K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28673K\"></sup>a foreigner to the speaker and the speaker a foreigner to me.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>So with yourselves, since you are eager for manifestations of the Spirit, strive to excel in building up the church.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Therefore, one who speaks in a tongue should pray that he may interpret.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For if I pray in a tongue, my spirit prays but my mind is unfruitful.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>What am I to do? I will pray with my spirit, but I will pray with my mind also; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28677L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28677L\"></sup>I will sing praise with my spirit, but I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28677M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28677M\"></sup>sing with my mind also.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Otherwise, if you give thanks with your spirit, how can anyone in the position of an outsider say <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28678N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28678N\"></sup>“Amen” to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28678O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28678O\"></sup>your thanksgiving when he does not know what you are saying?",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For you may be giving thanks well enough, but the other person is not being built up.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>I thank God that I speak in tongues more than all of you.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Nevertheless, in church I would rather speak five words with my mind in order to instruct others, than ten thousand words in a tongue.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Brothers, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28682P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28682P\"></sup>do not be children in your thinking. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28682Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28682Q\"></sup>Be infants in evil, but in your thinking be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28682R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28682R\"></sup>mature.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28683S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28683S\"></sup>In the Law it is written, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28683T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28683T\"></sup>“By people of strange tongues and by the lips of foreigners will I speak to this people, and even then they will not listen to me, says the Lord.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Thus tongues are a sign not for believers but for unbelievers, while prophecy is a sign not for unbelievers but for believers.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>If, therefore, the whole church comes together and all speak in tongues, and outsiders or unbelievers enter, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28685U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28685U\"></sup>will they not say that you are out of your minds?",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>But if all prophesy, and an unbeliever or outsider enters, he is convicted by all, he is called to account by all,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28687V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28687V\"></sup>the secrets of his heart are disclosed, and so, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28687W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28687W\"></sup>falling on his face, he will worship God and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28687X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28687X\"></sup>declare that God is really among you.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>What then, brothers? When you come together, each one has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28688Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28688Y\"></sup>a hymn, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28688Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28688Z\"></sup>a lesson, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28688AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28688AA\"></sup>a revelation, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28688AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28688AB\"></sup>a tongue, or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28688AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28688AC\"></sup>an interpretation. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28688AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28688AD\"></sup>Let all things be done for building up.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>If any speak in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28689AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28689AE\"></sup>a tongue, let there be only two or at most three, and each in turn, and let someone interpret.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>But if there is no one to interpret, let each of them keep silent in church and speak to himself and to God.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Let two or three prophets speak, and let the others <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28691AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28691AF\"></sup>weigh what is said.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>If a revelation is made to another sitting there, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28692AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28692AG\"></sup>let the first be silent.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>For you can all prophesy one by one, so that all may learn and all be encouraged,",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>and the spirits of prophets are subject to prophets.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>For God is not a God of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28695AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28695AH\"></sup>confusion but of peace.As in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28695AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28695AI\"></sup>all the churches of the saints,",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28696AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28696AJ\"></sup>the women should keep silent in the churches. For they are not permitted to speak, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28696AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28696AK\"></sup>should be in submission, as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28696AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28696AL\"></sup>the Law also says.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>If there is anything they desire to learn, let them ask their husbands at home. For it is shameful for a woman to speak in church.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>Or was it from you that the word of God came? Or are you the only ones it has reached?",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28699AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28699AM\"></sup>If anyone thinks that he is a prophet, or spiritual, he should acknowledge that the things I am writing to you are a command of the Lord.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>If anyone does not recognize this, he is not recognized.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>So, my brothers, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28701AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28701AN\"></sup>earnestly desire to prophesy, and do not forbid speaking in tongues.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28702AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28702AO\"></sup>But all things should be done decently and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28702AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28702AP\"></sup>in order."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">15 </span>Now I would remind you, brothers, of the gospel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28703A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28703A\"></sup>I preached to you, which you received, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28703B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28703B\"></sup>in which you stand,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and by which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28704C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28704C\"></sup>you are being saved, if you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28704D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28704D\"></sup>hold fast to the word I preached to you—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28704E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28704E\"></sup>unless you believed in vain.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28705F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28705F\"></sup>I delivered to you as of first importance what I also received: that Christ died <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28705G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28705G\"></sup>for our sins <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28705H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28705H\"></sup>in accordance with the Scriptures,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>that he was buried, that he was raised <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28706I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28706I\"></sup>on the third day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28706J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28706J\"></sup>in accordance with the Scriptures,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>and that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28707K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28707K\"></sup>he appeared to Cephas, then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28707L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28707L\"></sup>to the twelve.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Then he appeared to more than five hundred brothers at one time, most of whom are still alive, though some have fallen asleep.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Then he appeared to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28709M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28709M\"></sup>James, then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28709N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28709N\"></sup>to all the apostles.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Last of all, as to one untimely born, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28710O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28710O\"></sup>he appeared also to me.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28711P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28711P\"></sup>I am the least of the apostles, unworthy to be called an apostle, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28711Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28711Q\"></sup>I persecuted the church of God.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>But by the grace of God I am what I am, and his grace toward me was not in vain. On the contrary, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28712R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28712R\"></sup>I worked harder than any of them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28712S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28712S\"></sup>though it was not I, but the grace of God that is with me.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Whether then it was I or they, so we preach and so you believed.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Now if Christ is proclaimed as raised from the dead, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28714T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28714T\"></sup>how can some of you say that there is no resurrection of the dead?",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But if there is no resurrection of the dead, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28715U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28715U\"></sup>then not even Christ has been raised.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And if Christ has not been raised, then our preaching is in vain and your faith is in vain.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>We are even found to be misrepresenting God, because we testified about God that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28717V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28717V\"></sup>he raised Christ, whom he did not raise if it is true that the dead are not raised.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For if the dead are not raised, not even Christ has been raised.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And if Christ has not been raised, your faith is futile and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28719W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28719W\"></sup>you are still in your sins.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Then those also who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28720X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28720X\"></sup>have fallen asleep in Christ have perished.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>If in Christ we have hope in this life only, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28721Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28721Y\"></sup>we are of all people most to be pitied.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>But in fact <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28722Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28722Z\"></sup>Christ has been raised from the dead, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28722AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28722AA\"></sup>the firstfruits of those who have fallen asleep.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>For as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28723AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28723AB\"></sup>by a man came death, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28723AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28723AC\"></sup>by a man has come also the resurrection of the dead.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28724AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28724AD\"></sup>as in Adam all die, so also in Christ shall all be made alive.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>But each in his own order: Christ the firstfruits, then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28725AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28725AE\"></sup>at his coming <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28725AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28725AF\"></sup>those who belong to Christ.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Then comes the end, when he delivers <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28726AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28726AG\"></sup>the kingdom to God the Father after destroying <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28726AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28726AH\"></sup>every rule and every authority and power.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>For he must reign <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28727AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28727AI\"></sup>until he has put all his enemies under his feet.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>The last enemy to be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28728AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28728AJ\"></sup>destroyed is death.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28729AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28729AK\"></sup>“God has put all things in subjection under his feet.” But when it says, “all things are put in subjection,” it is plain that he is excepted who put all things in subjection under him.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>When <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28730AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28730AL\"></sup>all things are subjected to him, then the Son himself will also be subjected to him who put all things in subjection under him, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28730AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28730AM\"></sup>God may be all in all.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Otherwise, what do people mean by being baptized on behalf of the dead? If the dead are not raised at all, why are people baptized on their behalf?",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Why are we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28732AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28732AN\"></sup>in danger every hour?",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>I protest, brothers, by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28733AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28733AO\"></sup>my pride in you, which I have in Christ Jesus our Lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28733AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28733AP\"></sup>I die every day!",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>What do I gain if, humanly speaking, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28734AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28734AQ\"></sup>I fought with beasts at Ephesus? If the dead are not raised, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28734AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28734AR\"></sup>“Let us eat and drink, for tomorrow we die.”",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28735AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28735AS\"></sup>Do not be deceived: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28735AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28735AT\"></sup>“Bad company ruins good morals.”",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28736AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28736AU\"></sup>Wake up from your drunken stupor, as is right, and do not go on sinning. For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28736AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28736AV\"></sup>some have no knowledge of God. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28736AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28736AW\"></sup>I say this to your shame.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>But someone will ask, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28737AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28737AX\"></sup>“How are the dead raised? With what kind of body do they come?”",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>You foolish person! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28738AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28738AY\"></sup>What you sow does not come to life unless it dies.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>And what you sow is not the body that is to be, but a bare kernel, perhaps of wheat or of some other grain.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>But God gives it a body as he has chosen, and to each kind of seed its own body.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>For not all flesh is the same, but there is one kind for humans, another for animals, another for birds, and another for fish.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>There are heavenly bodies and earthly bodies, but the glory of the heavenly is of one kind, and the glory of the earthly is of another.",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>There is one glory of the sun, and another glory of the moon, and another glory of the stars; for star differs from star in glory.",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28744AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28744AZ\"></sup>So is it with the resurrection of the dead. What is sown is perishable; what is raised is imperishable.",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>It is sown in dishonor; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28745BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28745BA\"></sup>it is raised in glory. It is sown in weakness; it is raised in power.",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>It is sown a natural body; it is raised a spiritual body. If there is a natural body, there is also a spiritual body.",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>Thus it is written, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28747BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28747BB\"></sup>“The first man Adam became a living being”; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28747BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28747BC\"></sup>the last Adam became a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28747BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28747BD\"></sup>life-giving spirit.",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>But it is not the spiritual that is first but the natural, and then the spiritual.",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28749BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28749BE\"></sup>The first man was from the earth, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28749BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28749BF\"></sup>a man of dust; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28749BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28749BG\"></sup>the second man is from heaven.",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>As was the man of dust, so also are those who are of the dust, and as is the man of heaven, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28750BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28750BH\"></sup>so also are those who are of heaven.",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>Just <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28751BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28751BI\"></sup>as we have borne the image of the man of dust, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28751BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28751BJ\"></sup>we shall also bear the image of the man of heaven.",
			"50": "<sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup>I tell you this, brothers: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28752BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28752BK\"></sup>flesh and blood <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28752BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28752BL\"></sup>cannot inherit the kingdom of God, nor does the perishable inherit the imperishable.",
			"51": "<sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup>Behold! I tell you a mystery. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28753BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28753BM\"></sup>We shall not all sleep, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28753BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28753BN\"></sup>but we shall all be changed,",
			"52": "<sup class=\"versenum\">52 </sup>in a moment, in the twinkling of an eye, at the last trumpet. For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28754BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28754BO\"></sup>the trumpet will sound, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28754BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28754BP\"></sup>the dead will be raised imperishable, and we shall be changed.",
			"53": "<sup class=\"versenum\">53 </sup>For this perishable body must put on the imperishable, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28755BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28755BQ\"></sup>this mortal body must put on immortality.",
			"54": "<sup class=\"versenum\">54 </sup>When the perishable puts on the imperishable, and the mortal puts on immortality, then shall come to pass the saying that is written:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28756BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28756BR\"></sup>“Death is swallowed up in victory.”",
			"55": "<sup class=\"versenum\">55 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28757BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28757BS\"></sup>“O death, where is your victory?O death, where is your sting?”",
			"56": "<sup class=\"versenum\">56 </sup>The sting of death is sin, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28758BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28758BT\"></sup>the power of sin is the law.",
			"57": "<sup class=\"versenum\">57 </sup>But thanks be to God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28759BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28759BU\"></sup>who gives us the victory through our Lord Jesus Christ.",
			"58": "<sup class=\"versenum\">58 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28760BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28760BV\"></sup>Therefore, my beloved brothers, be steadfast, immovable, always abounding in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28760BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28760BW\"></sup>the work of the Lord, knowing that in the Lord <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28760BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28760BX\"></sup>your labor is not in vain."
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">16 </span>Now concerning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28761A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28761A\"></sup>the collection for the saints: as I directed the churches of Galatia, so you also are to do.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>On <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28762B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28762B\"></sup>the first day of every week, each of you is to put something aside and store it up, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28762C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28762C\"></sup>as he may prosper, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28762D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28762D\"></sup>so that there will be no collecting when I come.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And when I arrive, I will send <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28763E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28763E\"></sup>those whom you accredit by letter to carry your gift to Jerusalem.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>If it seems advisable that I should go also, they will accompany me.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28765F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28765F\"></sup>I will visit you after passing through <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28765G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28765G\"></sup>Macedonia, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28765H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28765H\"></sup>I intend to pass through Macedonia,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>and perhaps I will stay with you or even spend the winter, so that you may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28766I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28766I\"></sup>help me on my journey, wherever I go.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>For I do not want to see you now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28767J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28767J\"></sup>just in passing. I hope to spend some time with you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28767K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28767K\"></sup>if the Lord permits.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But I will stay in Ephesus until <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28768L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28768L\"></sup>Pentecost,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28769M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28769M\"></sup>a wide door for effective work has opened to me, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28769N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28769N\"></sup>there are many adversaries.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28770O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28770O\"></sup>When Timothy comes, see that you put him at ease among you, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28770P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28770P\"></sup>he is doing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28770Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28770Q\"></sup>the work of the Lord, as I am.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28771R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28771R\"></sup>let no one despise him. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28771S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28771S\"></sup>Help him on his way <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28771T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28771T\"></sup>in peace, that he may return to me, for I am expecting him with the brothers.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Now concerning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28772U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28772U\"></sup>our brother Apollos, I strongly urged him to visit you with the other brothers, but it was not at all his will to come now. He will come when he has opportunity.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28773V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28773V\"></sup>Be watchful, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28773W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28773W\"></sup>stand firm in the faith, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28773X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28773X\"></sup>act like men, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28773Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28773Y\"></sup>be strong.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28774Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28774Z\"></sup>Let all that you do be done in love.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Now I urge you, brothers—you know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28775AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28775AA\"></sup>the household of Stephanas were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28775AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28775AB\"></sup>the first converts in Achaia, and that they have devoted themselves <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28775AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28775AC\"></sup>to the service of the saints—",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28776AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28776AD\"></sup>be subject to such as these, and to every fellow worker and laborer.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>I rejoice at the coming of Stephanas and Fortunatus and Achaicus, because they have made up for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28777AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28777AE\"></sup>your absence,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>for they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28778AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28778AF\"></sup>refreshed my spirit as well as yours. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28778AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28778AG\"></sup>Give recognition to such people.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The churches of Asia send you greetings. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28779AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28779AH\"></sup>Aquila and Prisca, together with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28779AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28779AI\"></sup>the church in their house, send you hearty greetings in the Lord.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>All the brothers send you greetings. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28780AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28780AJ\"></sup>Greet one another with a holy kiss.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>I, Paul, write <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28781AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28781AK\"></sup>this greeting with my own hand.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>If anyone has no love for the Lord, let him be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28782AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28782AL\"></sup>accursed. Our Lord, come!",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28783AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28783AM\"></sup>The grace of the Lord Jesus be with you.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>My love be with you all in Christ Jesus. Amen."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;